message.content:
Isabel and Blanche were quick to sympathise and to
express their disgust at Sir John's abominable treatment
of his guest. But Piers remained aloof, and when Beryl
suggested having a second party, the following week, he
poured cold water on the project. Everyone, he declared,
had had a thoroughly good time, and it would take them
nearly to next week to settle down again. Meanwhile
theft would have betaken himself and his well-
earned gratuity to his native village at the
north of the island.
